snippet.title: Thoughts on Thursday Nancy Pelosi , Bernie Madoff , Amber Heard and Johnny Depp and IOWA Caucus Talk
snippet.description:
Thoughts on Thursdays, my first series! News of the week or things i find interesting with a free fun fact included. 
This week i’m tackling Nancy Pelosi’s tearing up of Trumps “Manifesto of Mistruths”, Bernie Madoff’s request to be released from prison because he’s dying, Johnny Depp and Amber Heards twisted toxic new turn in their ex-marriage and the shocking? surprising? troubling? IOWA Caucus results. 

Let me know your take! 
Like, Comment and Subscribe!
